data.description: Stunning home on nearly 7 acres! Step through the front doors into a spacious living space with an open floor plan kitchen and dining room, perfect for entertaining! The living room features a gorgeous brick fireplace perfect for cold winter days. Upstairs you will find the primary bedroom complete with a luxurious en suite with a freestanding tub and custom walk in shower. Three additional bedrooms upstairs as well as an office on the ground floor give you plenty of room to spread out. Outside you'll find a large covered patio overlooking a huge yard and a 20x40 10ft deep pool! Located on a dead end street and surround by trees, welcome to a serene slice of country life.
